sentence.Network_en: Directed by the warlike Inanna, he penetrates the Sinai peninsula, invades Egypt.
sentence.Network_cn: 受到好战的伊娜娜指引, 他渗透西奈半岛, 入侵埃及.

sentence.Network_en: Inanna's attempts to regain the kingship for Erech does not last.
sentence.Network_cn: 伊娜娜尝试去为伊里克夺得王权,但并不持续.

sentence.Network_en: As empire thrives, Shulgi falls under charms of Inanna, becomes her lover.
sentence.Network_cn: 因为帝国兴旺, 苏尔吉受到了伊娜娜的吸引力影响, 成为她的情人.
